    Simulated Example

    Simulated Example

    example.Rmd
    library(SPT.grpadalasso)
require(survival)
#> Loading required package: survival
    set.seed(123)

    Generate simulated data.

    df = 10
nn = 1000
beta = c(0.5,0,-0.5, rep(0,10))
sim_PO_data = PO.sim(nn, beta,
                     C.gen = function(n)
                       5+rbinom(n,1,0.5)*runif(n, -5, 0))
str(sim_PO_data)
